cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY 

The paper proposes a machine learning approach for predicting crowd flows in irregular regions of a city. The approach involves formulating the problem as a spatio-temporal graph prediction problem and using spatial graph convolution to build a multi-view graph convolutional network. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.SY (Systems and Control)
